                            <div class="info-box-info">
                                <h4 class="info-box-title">Developing Software</h4>
                                <p class="info-box-text text-gray-2">
                                    Upon a well estabished architecture, we create versatile algorithms that solve the real-world problems. 
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div> <!-- Developing Software -->
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="info-box info-box-4 info-box-white wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                            <span class="info-box-icon rounded-icon bg-main text-white"><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i></span>
                            <div class="info-box-info">
                                <h4 class="info-box-title">Maintainence</h4>
                                <p class="info-box-text text-gray-2">
                                    We issue a 1 year <b>free maintainence service</b> at the end of our all projects. All our
                                    software is delivered as open source.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div> <!-- Maintainence -->
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <a href="#modalServices" class="btn btn-white-bordered btn-rounded inline-popup-trigger pull-right"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Read More!</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div> <!-- Right column -->
        </div>
    </div>

